entries.entry: Today we introduced ourselves, met our instructors and were put into groups.
We worked on getting Vs Code set up on our laptops and how to access it through Terminal.
We went over the lightening exercises that we were given as homework.
We were given a project to do as a group today that is due in a few weeks. I am excited to see how it comes out!
We mostly worked with our groups today and decided what we would like our project to look like. I think it went well?
We learned how to push things up to our profile in GitHub and I think my brain is going to explode.
Today we presented our group project. I think we did really good! We were also assigned to a new group and I am excited to meet new people.
